      • leaveTimedZone

        public boolean leaveTimedZone(TimedZone timedZone,
                              EventToken eventToken)
        Evaluates whether an EventToken which previously entered a TimedZone is allowed to leave the zone, i.e. whether the (upper or lower) time constraint is satisfied or it is timed out.
        Parameters:
        timedZone - the TimedZone the EventToken attempts to leave
        eventToken - the EventToken attempting to leave the TimedZone
        Returns:
        whether the EventToken is allowed to leave the TimedZone or not
